g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驚無行人路要行馬路。貨車行得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60cf71afc3974484d590ed06885a98e2b4e0ea7e","tid":225880,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T06:40:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔行荔景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行過一次。要上山行好耐"},{"pid":"5caeaa44052516df868235d97b3c00f0b367aedb","tid":225880,"uid":32106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T06:41:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港地有咩地方行唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驚無行人路要行馬路。貨車行得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n青馬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e92d84176a682c2ce4d5fa05c53a91f9039278","tid":225880,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T06:50:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該"},{"pid":"dd6180401dd52ee9a308155f60d4741eac2db0ce","tid":225880,"uid":49055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T06:52:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港地有咩地方行唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驚無行人路要行馬路。貨車行得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n青馬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n行到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a873be1db319c204f62319c1cd8090815ab47b","tid":225880,"uid":76914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T06:57:33.000Z","msg":"貨櫃碼頭南路，全程有行人路"},{"pid":"ef31d9e0a87efa80ed322fd0094505ccfbec7e7f","tid":225880,"uid":40052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:01:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貨櫃碼頭南路，全程有行人路</blockquote><br />\n死氣廢氣專用區<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0709dfa49a4c75d6376546df86ffac1b4540fbf2","tid":225880,"uid":89923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:14:13.000Z","msg":"記住路係人行出黎既"},{"pid":"35dc93dc4b8bf2346cb2d7d41ece4a9c55f255fa","tid":225880,"uid":76914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:14:26.000Z","msg":"如果葵芳地鐵站開始，熟果頭都知有隧道過去 <strong>貨櫃碼頭路</strong>，然後 <strong>葵泰路</strong> &gt; <strong>貨櫃碼頭南路</strong>，去到昂船洲污水處理廠果頭入 <strong>興華街西</strong>，之後就會見到有條<strong>行人天橋</strong>橫越連翔道，一出道已經係南昌 <strong>深旺道</strong><br />\n<br />\n但第一次行要注意下邊啲位過馬路行對面行人路，因為有啲位會斷左一定要行第二邊，行得多就熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到好多人都唔識上荔景又落番美孚，都用唔少時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望多啲人見到多啲人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b872f22a8eac6107f2ac4e0de2fcc1faaa0068","tid":225880,"uid":76914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:16:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>貨櫃碼頭南路，全程有行人路</blockquote><br />\n死氣廢氣專用區<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下咩時間行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 經荔景出都要行長沙灣道果面，空氣都唔見好得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecfb2b2a52d6646007ff8f8cb39d16da60dccf3f","tid":225880,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:27:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果葵芳地鐵站開始，熟果頭都知有隧道過去 <strong>貨櫃碼頭路</strong>，然後 <strong>葵泰路</strong> &gt; <strong>貨櫃碼頭南路</strong>，去到昂船洲污水處理廠果頭入 <strong>興華街西</strong>，之後就會見到有條<strong>行人天橋</strong>橫越連翔道，一出道已經係南昌 <strong>深旺道</strong><br />\n<br />\n但第一次行要注意下邊啲位過馬路行對面行人路，因為有啲位會斷左一定要行第二邊，行得多就熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到好多人都唔識上荔景又落番美孚，都用唔少時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望多啲人見到多啲人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> mark 底下次放假試下 已經行上山路"},{"pid":"8d88fe2d30d2e0202e5a720c230dfe8b495a8be9","tid":225880,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:28:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果葵芳地鐵站開始，熟果頭都知有隧道過去 <strong>貨櫃碼頭路</strong>，然後 <strong>葵泰路</strong> &gt; <strong>貨櫃碼頭南路</strong>，去到昂船洲污水處理廠果頭入 <strong>興華街西</strong>，之後就會見到有條<strong>行人天橋</strong>橫越連翔道，一出道已經係南昌 <strong>深旺道</strong><br />\n<br />\n但第一次行要注意下邊啲位過馬路行對面行人路，因為有啲位會斷左一定要行第二邊，行得多就熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到好多人都唔識上荔景又落番美孚，都用唔少時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望多啲人見到多啲人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> mark 底下次放假試下 已經行上山路</blockquote><br />\n我上次就係唔識路，由荃灣西起步，最後摸上荔景山路由美孚出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過荔景山路都算幾好行，唔太斜。我估貨櫃碼頭路食塵會食得勁啲。"},{"pid":"4bddccd194e800d8cd827a86180337480b5378a0","tid":225880,"uid":96979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T09:03:23.000Z","msg":"先行去美孚再經長沙灣道會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}